  "title": "Systems Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1396963]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Take ownership of engineering design by accurately understanding client requirements and proposing solutions that meet technical specifications and project objectives.</li><li>Prepare and manage engineering documentation (VDRL), ensuring timely, accurate, and high-quality closure of client comments.</li><li>Produce conceptual and preliminary (“scratch”) drawings and guide AutoCAD drafters in delivering complete engineering drawing packages.</li><li>Apply relevant industry standards and best practices throughout engineering design, drawing preparation, review, and submission processes.</li><li>Guide in-house technicians on equipment assembly and cabinet integration, including system configuration, simulation, testing, and verification.</li><li>Conduct Factory Acceptance Testing (FAT) with clients and provide in-house training to clients and commissioning engineers.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>2 years of relevant experience in a similar engineering role within industrial markets.</li><li>Strong documentation skills with good time management and organizational abilities.</li><li>Ability to clearly articulate technical concepts and communicate effectively with customers and suppliers.</li><li>Proven ability to work cross-functionally and provide technical guidance or leadership within a team.</li><li>Results-driven, resourceful, and able to perform well in time-sensitive environments.</li></ul><p><strong>Added Advantages</strong></p><ul><li>Certification in AutoCAD.</li><li>Experience in site commissioning and/or radio surveying (e.g. SOLAS / MODU).</li><li>Proficiency with coverage and planning tools such as CadnaA (PAGA coverage), Ekahau (Wi-Fi coverage), and iBwave (UHF/GSM coverage)</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ong Kang Quan Ryan<br />EA Personnel Registration Number: R23116952<br />EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
